        <a href="calibration.html">Calibration</a>
        <a href="filament.html">Filament Management</a>
    </nav>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Filament Changing Procedure</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>Heat nozzle to 10°C above melting point</li>
            <li>Pull out remaining filament with pliers</li>
            <li>Clean the extruder gear and tube</li>
            <li>Load new filament slowly</li>
            <li>Perform a test print</li>
        </ol>
        <h3>Storage Recommendations</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Use desiccant packs in sealed containers</li>
            <li>Store away from direct sunlight</li>
            <li>Maintain humidity below 40%</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Common Issues</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Clogged nozzles: Clean with brass brush and heat</li>
            <li>Filament grinding: Check extruder tension and gear alignment</li>
            <li>Overshooting: Adjust flow rate settings</li>
        </ul>
